    <title mode="straight">
        <heading gtapi-trx-id="09e36daa-998f-4ff7-a931-40d210d3c77e" size="111" textalign="center" w="300" x="10">YOU CAN EXPRESS YOUR ATTITUDE TOWARDS GOD THROUGH PRAYER.</heading>
        <subheading gtapi-trx-id="5bcdf851-6ba4-452f-b5f8-3ed38758ce61" size="100" textalign="center">Prayer is simply talking with God.</subheading>
    </title>




    <text gtapi-trx-id="88a13a09-c5f6-4dd0-9fb3-88119738cf3c" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">Lord Jesus,</text><text gtapi-trx-id="453de523-1828-404b-be29-898ebc0bf8d5" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">I want to know you personally.</text><text gtapi-trx-id="f83226fc-3e6d-476e-a1fd-8b411b1cdcb3" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">I'm sorry for going my own way. Please forgive me for all my sin.</text><text gtapi-trx-id="8020a609-0984-43a7-81a8-be46cd573cc1" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">Thank you for dying on the cross to pay for my sin.</text><text gtapi-trx-id="74fa69ef-1a88-4fee-af2a-1b6884e6677c" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">I agree to turn from my old ways and follow you as my Saviour and Lord.</text><text gtapi-trx-id="4f1cebde-3801-4640-823e-7b90c8ed8cad" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20">Please come and take first place in my life.</text><text gtapi-trx-id="7d191d5f-5a8c-40e2-8bab-feef609adeaf" modifier="bold" size="110" textalign="left" x-trailing-offset="20" xoffset="20" yoffset="15">Is there anything stopping you from saying this right now?</text><button>
    <buttontext size="82">Did you pray this prayer?</buttontext>
    <panel>
